{"tid":729184,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜Keyman...（認真）","createTime":"2018-07-04T10:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T11:45:32.000Z","uid":163207,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"93318f5466147c55baa6b505f01d8b92ace808bf","tid":729184,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:38:46.000Z","msg":"細個開始睇波果陣好拎憎無線講波，覺得大鳩瑜、鳩猴忠、萬能鍾好拎廢（當年世界盃 Hacken一嘢叫俾啲時間阿叔食少少嘢），次次講波都好似教科書一般既戰術好悶<br />\n<br />\n到佢地退晒休，先知果D老練既旁述／分析係好野黎<br />\n<br />\n黃興桂既獨特痾屎唔出節奏、叻哥（全盛時期）既9 up、猁榮基對猁狗贏英超既執著，都係到退休／收左皮先發現佢地原來咁拎勁<br />\n<br />\n連登仔好多人都反Keyman，但係老實講佢既抽牙朗水技術、打J能力、對美斯既執著，冇人比得上佢（我覺得依家王騎&gt;&gt;Keyman）<br />\n<br />\n我諗Keyman最多都係講多1、2年就退休，其實聽得1場得1場，好好珍惜<br />\n<br />\n利申：廣東體育台年代何輝迷"},{"pid":"b402af2028eca534878fd668dde0cd39f6148127","tid":729184,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"講左咁多，原來吹奏何輝"},{"pid":"36a9a93562c57b7ca58c199ac7da7518e60c52cf","tid":729184,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b402af2028eca534878fd668dde0cd39f6148127","tid":729184,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"講左咁多，原來吹奏何輝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"keyman係青出於藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8686eff0e3c8c07050c39f6560a53491ae35e0","tid":729184,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"keyman&gt;&gt;&gt;何輝"},{"pid":"834b8ba7aa025ea90e85c951801b5c906221a3d7","tid":729184,"uid":516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:09:47.000Z","msg":"最撚憎中國輝"},{"pid":"0d47594b6b17e7f6a2bf873baaf34fd5ec07fe1d","tid":729184,"uid":4846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:18:04.000Z","msg":"丹尼爾，陳葦如 仲好過keyman <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364addb37ac512d9f9ba675b0dce9fd0e1066643","tid":7291